    "body": "@caperavensoftware I think you need to run your command within your PATH, so specifying the `env` option and setting the `PATH` in your exec call should fix the problem.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n```\r\nexec('command', {\r\n   env: { PATH: '/usr/local/bin/' }\r\n}, (error, stdout, stderr) => {});\r\n```"
