    "created_at": "2017-03-24T07:26:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-24T07:26:58Z",
    "body": "I had the same issue in our remote build scripts for MacOS, which behave differently from linux based systems. The way we solve it is prepend `export PATH=/usr/local/bin &&` to the command to be run (`npm init -y` here). This will guarantee the path will be available not only to the command but also to the sub-commands contained inside of it ..."
