    "body": "@caperavensoftware The issue is GUI apps on macOS don't inherit environment variables when packaged / distributed / not run from Terminal.\r\n\r\nThere is a module that fixes this for you however\r\n\r\nhttps://www.npmjs.com/package/fix-path"
